Monash Business School Journal Quality List

Source: R/data-monash.R
monash.Rd

This is a dataset that contains the list of quality journal rankings from the Monash Business School. In most cases, it follows ABDC with A* equal to Group 1 and A equal to Group 2. The "Group 1+" category contains a small set of the highest rank journals.

Usage

data(monash)

Format

An object of class tbl_df (inherits from tbl, data.frame) with 4617 rows and 2 columns.

Source

Monash Business School

Value

A data frame with 4617 observations on the following 2 variables:

title:

Title of the journal

rank:

In order of best to lowest rank: Group 1+, Group 1, Group 2

Examples

library(dplyr)
library(stringr)
monash |>
  filter(str_detect(title, "Statist")) |>
  arrange(rank)
#> # A tibble: 35 × 2
